https://www.graphql-ui-layout.com/* https://gem.zeropoint.bg/:splat 301!

# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.gem.zeropoint.bg/* https://gem.zeropoint.bg/:splat 301!

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://gem.zeropoint.bg/* https://gem.zeropoint.bg/:splat 301!

# Redirect old paths to new structure
